set view.characters.hobo.image = 'buttstacks'
set view.characters.hobo.name = 'Boris J. Buttstacks'

Hobo: Ahhh... my precious pickles. Not the ones I wanted, but close enough I suppose!

go menu

# menu
branch:
	- (if asked-what-type) go menu-where
	- (if asked-what-else) go menu-what-type
	- (default) go menu-what-else

# menu-what-else
Arca:
	- SKIP CONVERSATION -> skip
	- Ok... so is there anything else do you need me to get? -> what-else
	- (unless asked-which-onions) Huh? Which pickled onions did you want? -> which-onions
	- (unless onions-are-onions) A pickled onion is a pickled onion, Buttstacks -> onions-are-onions

# what-else
set asked-what-else
Hobo: Well as y’know I’m a bit of a celebrity, bein’ the mayor an’all...what can I say, it brings success with th'ladies! I got a date tonight with my best girl, an’ I wan'it to be perfect. So imma need some flowers. To woo her, get it? Dames love flowers. That and clocks.
go menu

# which-onions
set asked-which-onions
Hobo: Vintage '95. You got me Vintage '97. Not pungent enough for my sophisticated palate.
go menu

# onions-are-onions
set onions-are-onions
Hobo: You dunno what you're talkin' about. Although we can't all be pickled onion connessieurs
go menu

# menu-what-type
Arca:
	- What kind of flowers do you want?  -> what-type
	- (unless asked-clocks) Clocks? Why? -> clocks

# what-type
set asked-what-type
Hobo: Mmh. Y'know what? Get me a bunch o' the fluffiest dandelions you ever saw. They're like a man's heart y'know? The softest blow can destroy em'...
go menu

# clocks
set asked-clocks
Hobo: T'tell the time, why else d'ya think? Ya obviously ain't read Fellows are from Mongo, Fillies are from Marmington. Clueless critter.
go menu

# menu-where
Arca:
	- Okay... where can I find flowers? -> where
	- (unless asked-love) I'm sure she'll love them -> love
	- (unless asked-careful) Ok... I'll be very careful -> careful

# careful
set asked-careful
Hobo: Good. I want 'er to swoon at the sight of me holdin' 'em.
go menu
	
# love
set asked-love
Hobo: O'course she will. Much more subtle than poxy roses. 
go menu

# where
set asked-where
Hobo: Flee Market - here's the URL so you can find it.
go menu

